description:
This is a 7 minute workout called 'Beginner Bodyweight Workout in 5 Min' from the channel Jeffrey Peng MD.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This video is a 5 min beginner bodyweight workout routine. Exercises included in this video are:
Body weight squats
Calf raises
Hamstring curls
Seated straight leg raises
Push ups
Glute bridges
Plank

Muscle strengthening has incredible benefits to the body and improves our overall health. Do this routine once a day to build a foundation and then progress to more advanced exercises and longer routines. You can even do this routine twice or three times back to back for a better workout.
